textgoal: Define a function to repeat the function addOne x times on the number n
defines: ['function repeatAdd1(x, n) { return x == 0 ? n : addOne(repeatAdd1(x - 1, n)); }']

textgoal: Define a function to add a to n for x times (a * x + n)

textgoal: Define a function to apply the function f for x times on the input n
defines: ['function repeatFunction(x, n, f) { return x == 0 ? n : f(repeatFunction(x - 1, n, f)); }']
